Senior Surrey League Seasons

A brief sciencing of Surrey League (div 1) data:

I have had a go at making some funky plots from data from the last few Surrey League years (the data I have starts at the 2014⁄15 season). The plots are made from data from the wonderful Surrey League website and the google charts API (not mobile browser friendly, sorry!).

  • Season Points
  • Surrey Royalty

Season Points

There have been some tasty team battles over the years of the surrey league… the 2019 Senior Women battle between Herne Hill and Thames Hare and Hounds was close and came down to the final match. But not as close as the 2017⁄18 Men’s season between H/W and Kent AC.
